{"tid":658642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=大贈送？工廈保安巡樓  遭口罩男搶金鏈，揮拳施襲頭破血流","createTime":"2018-05-09T07:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T07:33:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4ed6ca07984b0c88ea626a9f477ca09c8bcce195","tid":658642,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T07:10:35.000Z","msg":"今日上午8時許，大角嘴福全街66號福全工廠大廈發生搶劫案！一名大廈男保安<span style=\"color: red;\">乘升降機巡查大廈時</span>，一名戴口罩的男子突然於升降機內，揮拳襲擊該名男保安，並搶走其一條金鏈，兇徒得手後逃去無蹤。該名男保安被打至頭破血流，其後由救護車送往醫院治理。警員到場兜截疑人無果，遂留守現場調查事件，並將該部升降機暫時封閉，現正追緝兇徒下落。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/186409/%E7%8B%A0%E8%B3%8A%E5%8A%AB%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89-%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%88%E5%8D%87%E9%99%8D%E6%A9%9F%E5%85%A7%E9%81%AD%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%94%B7%E6%90%B6%E9%87%91%E9%8F%88-%E6%8F%AE%E6%8B%B3%E6%96%BD%E8%A5%B2%E9%A0%AD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A1%80%E6%B5%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F186409%2F%25E7%258B%25A0%25E8%25B3%258A%25E5%258A%25AB%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25BB%2588%25E5%258D%2587%25E9%2599%258D%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%2590%25B6%25E9%2587%2591%25E9%258F%2588-%25E6%258F%25AE%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2596%25BD%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E8%25A1%2580%25E6%25B5%2581&d=tXfh0r%2FUpTK3OaQPDnQbR49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=208d6d84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/186409/%E7%8B%A0%E8%B3%8A%E5%8A%AB%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89-%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%88%E5%8D%87%E9%99%8D%E6%A9%9F%E5%85%A7%E9%81%AD%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%94%B7%E6%90%B6%E9%87%91%E9%8F%88-%E6%8F%AE%E6%8B%B3%E6%96%BD%E8%A5%B2%E9%A0%AD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A1%80%E6%B5%81</a>"},{"pid":"8dcefd8386b81e56a6b592b5fba4ec79f37d7dee","tid":658642,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T07:11:09.000Z","msg":"大出血"},{"pid":"b663a35cf003f016bb88c5e9cc13a7d24933e4a1","tid":658642,"